      <title>飓风米尔顿威胁佛罗里达州 300 亿美元市政债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/hurricane-milton-threatens-30-billion-of-muni-debt-in-florida</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博行业研究分析，随着飓风米尔顿袭击佛罗里达州并威胁到坦帕湾地区的巨大风暴潮，约有 300 亿美元的市政债务面临风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/hurricane-milton-threatens-30-billion-of-muni-debt-in-florida</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 17:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
